com.clover.sdk.util

Enum Platform

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Platform>
      • com.clover.sdk.util.Platform
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Platform>
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public enum Platform
extends Enum<Platform>
    Please discontinue using this class, it has been deprecated and will be deleted in a future version of the Clover Android SDK!

    Code which references this class almost certainly will not work on future Clover devices or even slight model variations.

    Clover frequently adds new models for existing devices when shipping devices to new regions. Please use Platform2 and/or relevant Android APIs to write code compatible with future devices that may have different screen sizes or hardware features.
